Synopsis:
   window new

Description:
   This creates a new TeKNap window.  This splits in half (vertically) either
   current window, or the largest.  
   By default, the new window will be created with the NOTIFY_LEVEL and
   HOLD_MODE settings.

See Also:
   set(4) always_split_biggest, hold_mode, notify_level; window(4) create,
   delete, kill, new_hide

